{
  "texts": [
    "LLM-based Written English EducationFor EFL students, good writing skill refers to the ability to effectively communicate ideas, thoughts, and information in written English, which plays an important role in EFL students' academic achievements.",
    "For EFL teachers, giving effective feedback on student writing is time-consuming, labor-intensive, and subjective.",
    "Furthermore, English language learners also face motivation issues and time constraints, limiting their ability to improve their writing skills [11].",
    "MMLs, especially ChatGPT, are seen as a possible solution to these problems by many educators.To investigate the influences of applying ChatGPT on EFL writing, much research has been done in recent years.",
    "The study from Song and Song investigated the effectiveness of ChatGPT writing aids by training Chinese EFL learners to pose inquiries, request clarification, or ask for additional examples and explanations from ChatGPT."
  ]
}